{"ID":"20220906204341-v3or88w","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906204341-v3or88w","title":"g-0分布式理论","type":"doc","updated":"20220906204341"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204342-ihi07k4","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906204342-ihi07k4","updated":"20220906204342"}},{"ID":"20220906204343-75piuq8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204343-75piuq8","updated":"20220906204343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7. 分布式","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204344-68tegi3","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204344-68tegi3","updated":"20220906204344"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204345-a7oz8d9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204345-a7oz8d9","updated":"20220906204345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204346-e26g455","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://www.yuque.com/docs/share/8a30ffb5-83f3-40f9-baf9-38de68b906dc\"\u003e\n            \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/xingqiu/xingqiu.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; width: 850px;\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/Snailclimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGithub\u003c/a\u003e |\n        \u003ca href=\"https://gitee.com/SnailClimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGitee\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204346-e26g455","updated":"20220906204346"}},{"ID":"20220906204347-ccikrod","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204347-ccikrod","updated":"20220906204347"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.1 理论\u0026算法\u0026协议","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204348-luctsi0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204348-luctsi0","updated":"20220906204348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是 CAP理论？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204349-kbn2wxu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204349-kbn2wxu","updated":"20220906204349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/CAP定理","TextMarkTextContent":"CAP 理论/定理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"起源于 2000年，由加州大学伯克利分校的Eric Brewer教授在分布式计算原理研讨会（PODC）上提出，因此 CAP定理又被称作 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"布鲁尔定理（Brewer’s theorem）"}]},{"ID":"20220906204350-e8vwwma","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204350-e8vwwma","updated":"20220906204350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2年后，麻省理工学院的Seth Gilbert和Nancy Lynch 发表了布鲁尔猜想的证明，CAP理论正式成为分布式领域的定理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204351-7w2ch2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204351-7w2ch2g","updated":"20220906204351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"CAP"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 也就是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Consistency（一致性）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Availability（可用性）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Partition Tolerance（分区容错性）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 这三个单词首字母组合。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204352-opdgn1i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204352-opdgn1i","updated":"20220906204352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"img","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/2020-11/cap.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204353-w0vars7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204353-w0vars7","updated":"20220906204353"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CAP 理论的提出者布鲁尔在提出 CAP 猜想的时候，并没有详细定义 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Consistency"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Availability"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Partition Tolerance"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 三个单词的明确定义。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204354-rn2zd1z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204354-rn2zd1z","updated":"20220906204354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，对于 CAP 的民间解读有很多，一般比较被大家推荐的是下面 👇 这种版本的解读。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204355-isvjevj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204355-isvjevj","updated":"20220906204355"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在理论计算机科学中，CAP 定理（CAP theorem）指出对于一个分布式系统来说，当设计读写操作时，只能同时满足以下三点中的两个：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204356-gpguvvn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204356-gpguvvn","updated":"20220906204356"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204357-vc7uuru","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204357-vc7uuru","updated":"20220906204357"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204358-3hjvwes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204358-3hjvwes","updated":"20220906204358"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一致性（Consistency）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 所有节点访问同一份最新的数据副本","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204359-8nph488","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204359-8nph488","updated":"20220906204359"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204360-jqdr3zw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204360-jqdr3zw","updated":"20220906204360"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可用性（Availability）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 非故障的节点在合理的时间内返回合理的响应（不是错误或者超时的响应）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204361-fygen6z","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204361-fygen6z","updated":"20220906204361"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204362-oppd7cd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204362-oppd7cd","updated":"20220906204362"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分区容错性（Partition tolerance）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" : 分布式系统出现网络分区的时候，仍然能够对外提供服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204363-x696ny3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204363-x696ny3","updated":"20220906204363"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"什么是网络分区？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204364-tiq3y1c","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204364-tiq3y1c","updated":"20220906204364"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204365-3hqmii0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204365-3hqmii0","updated":"20220906204365"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式系统中，多个节点之前的网络本来是连通的，但是因为某些故障（比如部分节点网络出了问题）某些节点之间不连通了，整个网络就分成了几块区域，这就叫网络分区。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204366-wqashm1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204366-wqashm1","updated":"20220906204366"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"partition-tolerance","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/2020-11/partition-tolerance.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204367-1ff31uk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204367-1ff31uk","updated":"20220906204367"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大部分人解释这一定律时，常常简单的表述为：“一致性、可用性、分区容忍性三者你只能同时达到其中两个，不可能同时达到”。实际上这是一个非常具有误导性质的说法，而且在 CAP 理论诞生 12 年之后，CAP 之父也在 2012 年重写了之前的论文。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204368-a08y7lp","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204368-a08y7lp","updated":"20220906204368"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204369-yn9ivdy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204369-yn9ivdy","updated":"20220906204369"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"当发生网络分区的时候，如果我们要继续服务，那么强一致性和可用性只能 2 选 1。也就是说当网络分区之后 P 是前提，决定了 P 之后才有 C 和 A 的选择。也就是说分区容错性（Partition tolerance）我们是必须要实现的。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204370-71wogh9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204370-71wogh9","updated":"20220906204370"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简而言之就是：CAP 理论中分区容错性 P 是一定要满足的，在此基础上，只能满足可用性 A 或者一致性 C。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204371-eo55fqi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204371-eo55fqi","updated":"20220906204371"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分布式系统理论上不可能选择 CA 架构，只能选择 CP 或者 AP 架构。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 比如 ZooKeeper、HBase 就是 CP 架构，Cassandra、Eureka 就是 AP 架构，Nacos 不仅支持 CP 架构也支持 AP 架构。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204372-zxojfmr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204372-zxojfmr","updated":"20220906204372"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为啥不可能选择 CA 架构呢？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 举个例子：若系统出现“分区”，系统中的某个节点在进行写操作。为了保证 C， 必须要禁止其他节点的读写操作，这就和 A 发生冲突了。如果为了保证 A，其他节点的读写操作正常的话，那就和 C 发生冲突了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204373-v239nph","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204373-v239nph","updated":"20220906204373"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"选择 CP 还是 AP 的关键在于当前的业务场景，没有定论，比如对于需要确保强一致性的场景如银行一般会选择保证 CP 。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204374-ad895bu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204374-ad895bu","updated":"20220906204374"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，需要补充说明的一点是： ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如果网络分区正常的话（系统在绝大部分时候所处的状态），也就说不需要保证 P 的时候，C 和 A 能够同时保证。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204375-zs0xwxg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204375-zs0xwxg","updated":"20220906204375"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么是 Base 理论？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204376-ktmiofg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204376-ktmiofg","updated":"20220906204376"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/1394127.1394128","TextMarkTextContent":"BASE 理论"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"起源于 2008 年， 由eBay的架构师Dan Pritchett在ACM上发表。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204377-m1exp2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204377-m1exp2p","updated":"20220906204377"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"BASE"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Basically Available（基本可用）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Soft-state（软状态）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Eventually Consistent（最终一致性）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 三个短语的缩写。BASE 理论是对 CAP 中一致性 C 和可用性 A 权衡的结果，其来源于对大规模互联网系统分布式实践的总结，是基于 CAP 定理逐步演化而来的，它大大降低了我们对系统的要求。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204378-6dr009k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204378-6dr009k","updated":"20220906204378"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"即使无法做到强一致性，但每个应用都可以根据自身业务特点，采用适当的方式来使系统达到最终一致性。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204379-ux2u0f0","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204379-ux2u0f0","updated":"20220906204379"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204380-jocjehf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204380-jocjehf","updated":"20220906204380"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也就是牺牲数据的一致性来满足系统的高可用性，系统中一部分数据不可用或者不一致时，仍需要保持系统整体“主要可用”。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204381-wby4id8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204381-wby4id8","updated":"20220906204381"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"BASE 理论本质上是对 CAP 的延伸和补充，更具体地说，是对 CAP 中 AP 方案的一个补充。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204382-ficifpb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204382-ficifpb","updated":"20220906204382"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为什么这样说呢？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204383-mxxwmdl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204383-mxxwmdl","updated":"20220906204383"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CAP 理论这节我们也说过了：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204384-d919jp4","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204384-d919jp4","updated":"20220906204384"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204385-jm278ni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204385-jm278ni","updated":"20220906204385"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果系统没有发生“分区”的话，节点间的网络连接通信正常的话，也就不存在 P 了。这个时候，我们就可以同时保证 C 和 A 了。因此，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如果系统发生“分区”，我们要考虑选择 CP 还是 AP。如果系统没有发生“分区”的话，我们要思考如何保证 CA 。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204386-wihtd2z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204386-wihtd2z","updated":"20220906204386"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，AP 方案只是在系统发生分区的时候放弃一致性，而不是永远放弃一致性。在分区故障恢复后，系统应该达到最终一致性。这一点其实就是 BASE 理论延伸的地方。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204387-rgo1d5x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204387-rgo1d5x","updated":"20220906204387"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聊聊你对 Paxos 算法的了解？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204388-4as1z3q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204388-4as1z3q","updated":"20220906204388"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Paxos 算法是兰伯特在 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1990"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 年提出了一种分布式系统共识算法。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204389-ky6vi5z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204389-ky6vi5z","updated":"20220906204389"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"兰伯特当时提出的 Paxos 算法主要包含 2 个部分:","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204390-7uhbgqp","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204390-7uhbgqp","updated":"20220906204390"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204391-gdp4wf7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204391-gdp4wf7","updated":"20220906204391"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204392-nfh0ere","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204392-nfh0ere","updated":"20220906204392"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Basic Paxos 算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 描述的是多节点之间如何就某个值(提案 Value)达成共识。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204393-lg5mnwk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204393-lg5mnwk","updated":"20220906204393"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204394-vgvavt7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204394-vgvavt7","updated":"20220906204394"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Multi-Paxos 思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 描述的是执行多个 Basic Paxos 实例，就一系列值达成共识。Multi-Paxos 说白了就是执行多次 Basic Paxos ，核心还是 Basic Paxos 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204395-67xa3wz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204395-67xa3wz","updated":"20220906204395"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于 Paxos 算法在国际上被公认的非常难以理解和实现，因此不断有人尝试简化这一算法。到了2013 年才诞生了一个比 Paxos 算法更易理解和实现的共识算法—","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/distributed-system/theorem\u0026algorithm\u0026protocol/raft-algorithm.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Raft 算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。更具体点来说，Raft 是Multi-Paxos的一个变种，其简化了 Multi-Paxos 的思想，变得更容易被理解以及工程实现。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204396-5yohcyg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204396-5yohcyg","updated":"20220906204396"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 Paxos 算法的详细介绍，请看","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/distributed-system/theorem\u0026algorithm\u0026protocol/paxos-algorithm.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Paxos 算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这篇文章。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204397-nqtmo0x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204397-nqtmo0x","updated":"20220906204397"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"聊聊你对 Raft 算法的了解？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204398-lkp015m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204398-lkp015m","updated":"20220906204398"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/distributed-system/theorem\u0026algorithm\u0026protocol/raft-algorithm.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Raft 算法"}]},{"ID":"20220906204399-9oh4x2z","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906204399-9oh4x2z","updated":"20220906204399"}}]}